# Production Environment Variables
# =================================

# Security & Authentication
JWT_SECRET=your-super-strong-jwt-secret-key-change-this-in-production-256-bits
CLI_API_KEY=your-secure-cli-api-key-change-this-in-production

# Database Configuration
